Facilyn: I'm fortunate to have traveled many places. And in most places, what I saw was the same: Good meaning people trying their best, and yet the problems were getting more, not less.

She adjusts her patched satchel.

Facilyn: Then I was given the chance to work with others—people from all kinds of backgrounds—digging deeper into the issue. We were brought together by one incredibly determined individual. When we finally broke through, we created a framework that helps manage complexity.

